com.example.federico.wearableui.intraprocess_messaging

Class IPMHCallbackInterface

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.federico.wearableui.intraprocess_messaging.IPMHCallbackInterface
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ViewportActivity

    public abstract class IPMHCallbackInterface
extends java.lang.Object
    Interface that defines the callbacks used to handle the messages received by the IntraProcessMessageHandler.
